Ques-2 Food Delivery Pricing System (Swiggy/Zomato-like)
-----------------------------------------------------------------------

You are building a Food Delivery System where delivery charges vary based on delivery type.


🚚 Delivery Types:
------------------------
Normal Delivery:
₹30 base + ₹5 per km
Fast Delivery:
₹50 base + ₹10 per km
Scheduled Delivery:
₹20 base + ₹4 per km (discounted)

🏗️ Classes & Variables:
------------------------------
1. Interface: DeliveryChargeStrategy
double calculateCharge(double distance);
2. Concrete Classes:
NormalDelivery
Variables:
double baseCharge = 30
double perKm = 5
FastDelivery
Variables:
double baseCharge = 50
double perKm = 10
ScheduledDelivery
Variables:
double baseCharge = 20
double perKm = 4
3. Context Class: DeliveryService
Variables:
DeliveryChargeStrategy strategy
Methods:
setStrategy(DeliveryChargeStrategy strategy)
calculateTotal(double distance)
4. AppConfig Class:
Define beans for all strategies
Inject into DeliveryService
Support runtime switching

